</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_317" id="157v"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee">
<ab><expan>H<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>Otte<ex>n</ex></expan> von Milcz, tumprobst czu
                                <expan>Wirczb<ex>ur</ex>g</expan> und czu Bamberg tumherren</ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab><expan>Erwirdig<ex>er</ex></expan> und lieber <expan>h<ex>er</ex>re</expan>,
                        uns <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>fürg<ex>elegt</ex></expan> Fridrich Pyrkheymer und <expan cert="unknown">S.</expan>
<expan>Gewd<ex>er</ex></expan>, <expan>uns<ex>e</ex>r</expan>
<expan>burge<ex>r</ex></expan>, von iren und etlicher anderr
                                <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>r</expan>
<expan>burge<ex>r</ex></expan> und irer armenlewte wegen czu Herperstorff,
                        Understorff und Yllhofen, wie ir <expan>dieselb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> ir
                        armlewte für geistlich geriht gen <expan>Bamb<ex>er</ex>g</expan> geladen
                        habt von ungewonlichs <expan>czehend<ex>en</ex></expan> wegen, den sie noch
                        ir <expan>vord<ex>er</ex>n</expan> vormals nye
                            <expan>gegeb<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan>. <expan>Ro<ex>gamus</ex></expan>, daz
                                <expan>dieselb<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex>r</expan> burger armlewte mit
                            <expan>söliche<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>ungewonliche<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>czehend<ex>en</ex></expan> unbesweret und sie damit
                                <expan>beleib<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>lasze<ex>n</ex></expan> wollet, als sie und ir vordern von alter
                                <expan>herküme<ex>n</ex></expan> sein, möht aber des niht gesein,
                        daz ir doch das einen monad <add>oder lenger</add>
<expan>aufslah<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wöllet, <expan>wan<ex>n</ex></expan> sich
                                <expan>dieselb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> armlewte von unfrids und
                                <expan>nötlich<ex>er</ex></expan> sache wegen darümb
                                    <add><expan>yeczund<ex>en</ex></expan></add> niht wol
                                <expan>v<ex>er</ex>antwurtten</expan>
<expan>müge<ex>n</ex></expan>. Und wöllet euch hierynne
                            <expan>d<ex>ur</ex>h</expan>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>wille<ex>n</ex></expan> beweisen als etc. Das
                            <expan>wölle<ex>n</ex></expan> etc. <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan>
<expan>fe<ex>ri</ex>a</expan> iii <expan>p<ex>ost</ex></expan>
<expan>nati<ex>vita</ex><hi rend="sup">t<ex>is</ex>
</hi></expan>
<expan>s<ex>an</ex>c<ex>t</ex>e</expan> Marie
                            <expan>virg<ex>in</ex>is</expan> anno xxi<hi rend="sup">o</hi>.</ab>
</div>
